%^BOLD%^-=%^YELLOW%^Knowledge Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Deities that grant the knowledge domain are masters of
knowledge themselves.  They implant certain learning into
the minds of their followers, even if for only a short time.
This knowledge may aid the caster in communication, skills,
and may even be turned against a foe.

The knowledge domain contains the following spells:
Comprehend Languages (3rd), Wieldskill (5th), and Forgotten Melody (7th)

True Strike, Detect Thoughs*, Tongues, Deathward, False Vision, Legend Lore, Powerword Blind

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Kismet

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
